{"tid":1402401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線義士返到屋企見到3000幾正評話佢地抵死會點諗？","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:15:11.000Z","uid":38548,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1934d197ee12b7b260f0321fa0ae0387c6110270","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:14:14.000Z","msg":"就算幾蠢幾錯都好<br />\n如果有真係同路人 又係企前線  <br />\n就咁見到個topic  +  3000幾正評佢地會有咩感受<br />\n<br />\n已經唔係要你完全理解佢地處境<br />\n資訊幾唔流通 情況幾迷茫  食左幾粒彈食到真係懵左<br />\n咁就要話佢地抵死？<br />\n<br />\n我冇意要分前線定唔係前線<br />\n有同一信念就係自己<br />\n唔係個個都可以用上帝視角睇大局<br />\n<br />\n總之為左抗爭俾人拉 用青春 前途黎做代價<br />\n無論咩原因都唔可以貶低佢地既付出"},{"pid":"d4b90a58e3ace30cd5fafccea23c4b671ade9e00","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"鬼俾人拉 唔會有事<br />\n真義士因為現場情況混亂反應唔到 俾人拉坐五六七年<br />\n<br />\n抵死？"},{"pid":"d8e614018210554a57acb9e171be0ad77cec178b","tid":1402401,"uid":133903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"我向前線義士講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520325a9de408d471833ac6b8e916d9d6a871495","tid":1402401,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f4b52e08ec533bccdf2e7013620954c65ed1a8","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:18:52.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解有人撳正評撳得落手<br />\n<br />\n我更加唔明點解有人講得出口<br />\n<br />\n講左就算 正評左都算<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家自己人唔好再分化<br />\n<br />\n同路人前唔前線都一樣係自己人"},{"pid":"08876f9b22a3e9ec53a4610effcd9aaf5209f540","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"企左係前方既義士見到個post 都請唔好灰心<br />\n<br />\n大家都知支那維穩機器已經發動 分分鐘有大半正評都係鬼鼠數<br />\n<br />\n我都相信你地係為信念而戰 唔係為其他人係網上講幾句認同自己"},{"pid":"4b8cd93a307d1f1ddaa358eb81563434070f8585","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:23:18.000Z","msg":"有巴打講得好啱<br />\n<br />\n只有廢老 藍絲 狗 先會認為為抗爭俾人拉係抵死"},{"pid":"c5dbfadc2652e374e843a0e9df497c1b1f0a6122","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"再講<br />\n<br />\n個post 後期大部份人都comment 屌鳩返樓主<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似前線情況 連登一樣<br />\n<br />\n頭先一堆屌鳩自己人post 出現 大家都會混亂 所以希望大家都應該互相體諒 <br />\n<br />\n但冇一個自己人係抵死"},{"pid":"5b20ae5022d32440af0e9f2ece989e2e067594f8","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5dbfadc2652e374e843a0e9df497c1b1f0a6122","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"再講<br />\n<br />\n個post 後期大部份人都comment 屌鳩返樓主<br />\n<br />\n情況就好似前線情況 連登一樣<br />\n<br />\n頭先一堆屌鳩自己人post 出現 大家都會混亂 所以希望大家都應該互相體諒 <br />\n<br />\n但冇一個自己人係抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"推返上去俾正評班人睇到"},{"pid":"803029db2488091ae448cfdbaac67ca257ff0da8","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"冇其他人回都照推"},{"pid":"7852d5d9bdabe09ba79f6e3fd8ba306b5c11910f","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:35:39.000Z","msg":"分化post 永遠推得快"},{"pid":"ad953910521531168a44b1538aeb293585de04b3","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad6270fa036fd1205a11b715fea5b2a5678fa9bc","tid":1402401,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit